# my.removeStorageSync

2021-05-09 18:43

Remove cached data synchronously.

> This is a synchronous interface.

## Sample Code

copy

```javascript
my.removeStorageSync({
  key: 'currentCity',
});
```

## Parameters

|     |     |     |     |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Property** | **Type** | **Required** | **Description** |
| key | String | Yes | Cache data key. |
